      "content": "but medical stuff doesnt even touch this anymore. it's just... it feels like my body is an enemy at this point. i've tried everything they suggest and it just doesnt work. the doctors just talk about management, but how do you manage something that makes you want to scream every single minute? it feels less like an illness and more like a sentence. like, is there actually any point in trying to \"manage\" a life that's just constant agony?",
